        <h4 class="header">Combinations</h4>
        <h6 class="subheader thin no-margin">Mix and match the <code class="inline">.rounded</code>, <code class="inline">.inverted</code>, and <code class="inline">.bordered</code> classes to create the perfect pagination.</h6>
